      "description": [
        "{{sbc|Innate:}} Upon taking {{tip|death|fatal damage}}, '''Karthus''' enters {{tip|Zombie state}} for 7 seconds, where he can cast his abilities at no cost but is unable to move. If {{ai|Defile|Karthus}} has been learned, it will remain toggled on for ''Death Defied's'' entire duration. {{ai|Requiem|Karthus}} becomes disabled after ''Death Defied'' has lasted 4 seconds.",
        "{{sbc|{{tip|Zombie State|nolink=true|notip=true}}:}} During '''Zombie state''', '''Karthus''' is {{tip|invulnerability|invulnerable}}, {{tip|untargetable}}, and {{tip|cc-immune|immune to crowd control}}, but unable to [[basic attack]], cast [[champion ability|abilities]], use [[summoner spell]]s or [[active ability items|activate items]]."
      ],
      "descriptionHtml": "<span class=\"sbc\">Innate:</span> Upon taking <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">fatal damage<template #content><div><h4>death<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword death</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>, <b>Karthus</b> enters <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">Zombie state<template #content><div><h4>Zombie state<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword Zombie state</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip> for 7 seconds, where he can cast his abilities at no cost but is unable to move. If <span class=\"ai\">Karthus's Defile</span> has been learned, it will remain toggled on for <i>Death Defied's</i> entire duration. <span class=\"ai\">Karthus's Requiem</span> becomes disabled after <i>Death Defied</i> has lasted 4 seconds.<br /><span class=\"sbc\"><HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">Zombie State<template #content><div><h4>Zombie State<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword Zombie State</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>:</span> During <b>Zombie state</b>, <b>Karthus</b> is <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">invulnerable<template #content><div><h4>invulnerability<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword invulnerability</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>, <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">untargetable<template #content><div><h4>untargetable<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword untargetable</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>, and <HtmlTooltip class=\"blue link\">immune to crowd control<template #content><div><h4>cc-immune<hr></h4><p>Description for keyword cc-immune</p></div></template></HtmlTooltip>, but unable to <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"basic attack\">basic attack</a>, cast <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"abilities\">champion ability</a>, use <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"summoner spell\">summoner spell</a>s or <a class=\"effect link\" title=\"activate items\">active ability items</a>.",
      "leveling": [],
      "notes": "* ''Death Defied's'' {{tip|untargetability}} does not {{tip|homing projectile destruction|destroy}} in-flight {{tip|projectiles}}.\n* '''Karthus''' cannot be {{tip|execute|executed}} by the {{bi|Aspect of the Dragon}} during ''Death Defied''.\n* At the start of ''Death Defied'', '''Karthus''' is set to {{sti|health|{{as|1 health}}}}.\n** '''Karthus''' can still regenerate his health over the duration, but he will always die at the end of it.\n* After ''Death Defied'' ends, the corpse of '''Karthus''' will retain [[unit collision]] despite being dead on the ground.\n* '''Karthus' ''' [[health bar|mana bar]] drains over the duration of ''Death Defied'' as an indicator of his time remaining in this state.\n{{Zombie state info}}",
      "skillkey": "I",
      "skillid": "i1",
      "effects": []
    },
